## Summary: Theoretical Predictions vs. Empirical Results

| Prediction | Status | Key Evidence |
|------------|--------|--------------|
| **Balance Schema in Friendship** | ✅ Confirmed | Elevated C-FP and P-FP motifs (Z > 2.0) |
| **Asymmetric Recognition in Advice** | ✅ Confirmed | Higher accuracy, better model fit |
| **Individual Heterogeneity** | ✅ Confirmed | 3-fold variation in accuracy rates |
| **Self vs. Proxy Differences** | ✅ Confirmed | Self-report 15-25% more accurate |
| **Complex Density Effects** | ⚠️ Partial | Non-linear patterns, context-dependent |
| **Mixed False Motifs** | ✅ Novel Finding | Individual-level directional confusion |

